<td align=right id=headerrow valign=bottom><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=88126><span id= >Neiph</span></a>, <span id= > </span><br><span id=notbold>1 posts</td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Mon, Aug 20th 10:21 PM 2001</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent<span id=notbold>[3.00]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>I started my first character ever to exist yesterday. This character is a Dark Elf Necromancer. I am a level 3 and I constantly die because of getting lost, etc. Luckily I have the spell making me capable to find my corpses when I die, but I am having trouble leveling. So, I am looking for anybody willing to help me level at all. I'm on the Lanys T`vyl server. I'm located in Neriak. If anybody is willing, please email me at metaliknight@hotmail.com<br><br>Thank you very much.<br>&nbsp;<br>"Just like Winnie the Pooh."; Jay, of "Jay and Silent Bob Strike Back"</td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 >&nbsp;</td><td align=right valign=bottom>
